<br>
 I have never tried this pre-level 45, so Im not sure how it works at lower levels. I really wish I knew this way back when, and trying to break linked mobs from a camp.<br>
<br>
I have recently been soloing at the Entrance to the Hole. There are 7 mobs there. Id say 5 of them linked with the last 2 linked with themselves. I can without fail clear this spawn area using Nullify, it does not aggro anything other then the mob thats is targeted.<br>
<br>
 Im sure im not the first one to notice this, but Im wondering if it works at lower levels and if so, why havent we heard about it more?<br>
<br>
 Why is it not in a Breaking spawns 101 tactic somewhere?<br>
<br>
 For the record, these mobs are mostly blue to me, while a few are green now its mostly blue city. Im not sure how it would work on yellows or reds.<br>
<br>
<br>
Anyone else here have more info to add?<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
[52 Elementalist] Zandar (Human) &lt;Companions of the Gate&gt; - Bristlebane<br>
